#. js-lingui-id: HP7per
#: src/pages/settings/applications/utils/getStandardApplicationDescription.ts
msgid ""
"The base data model every Twenty workspace runs on.\n"
"\n"
"#### What \"foundation\" means\n"
"\n"
"Every Twenty workspace starts with this set of objects. They define the shape of your CRM, including relationships, activity, and reporting. Everything else, including marketplace apps, AI agents, and custom objects, plugs into them.\n"
"\n"
"#### Included objects\n"
"- **People & Companies**: contact and account records\n"
"- **Opportunities**: your sales pipeline\n"
"- **Notes & Tasks**: activity and follow-ups\n"
"- **Workflows & Dashboards**: automation and reporting\n"
"\n"
"Remove this app and the rest of Twenty has nothing to hang off.\n"
"\n"
"#### Build your own app\n"
"\n"
"Extend Twenty with your own objects, fields, logic functions, or AI skills. Scaffold a new app in one command:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Then inside the folder:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"See the [Getting Started guide](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) for the full walkthrough, and [Building Apps](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) for the `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` APIs."
msgstr ""
"Het basisdatamodel waarop elke Twenty-werkruimte draait.\n"
"\n"
"#### Wat \"fundament\" betekent\n"
"\n"
"Elke Twenty-werkruimte begint met deze set objecten. Ze bepalen de vorm van je CRM, inclusief relaties, activiteiten en rapportage. Al het andere, waaronder marketplace-apps, AI-agents en aangepaste objecten, haakt daarop in.\n"
"\n"
"#### Inbegrepen objecten\n"
"- **Personen & bedrijven**: contact- en accountrecords\n"
"- **Kansen**: je verkooppijplijn\n"
"- **Notities & taken**: activiteiten en opvolging\n"
"- **Werkstromen & dashboards**: automatisering en rapportage\n"
"\n"
"Verwijder deze app en de rest van Twenty heeft niets meer om op te steunen.\n"
"\n"
"#### Bouw je eigen app\n"
"\n"
"Breid Twenty uit met je eigen objecten, velden, logische functies of AI-vaardigheden. Maak de basis voor een nieuwe app aan met één commando:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"npx create-twenty-app@latest my-twenty-app\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Ga vervolgens naar de map:\n"
"\n"
"```bash\n"
"cd my-twenty-app\n"
"yarn twenty dev\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"Zie de [Aan de slag-gids](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/getting-started) voor de volledige rondleiding, en [Apps bouwen](https://twenty.com/developers/extend/apps/building) voor de `defineApplication` / `defineEntity` API's."

